additional_info:
Use the following colors in the blackboard color editor:

Page background: #000000
Background for columns A and C: #181818
Header background for columns A and C and header text for column B: #FFF040
Header text for columns A and C and header background for column B: #181818
Text for columns A and C: #FFF25B
Link for columns A and C: #FFE62B
Border for column B: #181818




Optional code for Welcome Bar: 
"

.contextbar td{
     background-color: #000000 !important;
     text-align: center !important;
}

.activesubtab {
     color: #FFE62B !important;
     padding-left:200px !important;
}

.contextbar td a:link{
     color: #FFE62B !important;
     text-decoration: none !important;
     text-align: center !important;
}

.contextbar td a:hover{
     color: #fffa8a !important;
     text-decoration: underline !important;
}

.contextbar td img {
     display:none !important;
     
}

.contextbar td a.mywebctlinks:after{
     content:"|";
     
}

.contextbar td a.inline img {
     display:inline!important;
     background-color: #000000 !important;
     border:none !important;
}

.contextbar td a{
     background-color: #000000 !important;
     border:none !important;
     padding: 1px !important;
}

.contextbar td a.inline:link, .contextbar td a.inline:visited, .contextbar td a.inline:active{
    background: #000000 !important;
}
